<D>__{first a wire.}
<C>__{doyle}
<D>__{two wires. one on the store and one on his house.}
<C>__{simonson}
<D>__{you know i have to get a court order for wiretaps.}
<C>__{russo}
<D>__{try... okay?}
<C>__{doyle}
<D>__{we know you can do it, walter.}
